sentences: Her output was not particularly large and most of her works were written between 1914 and 1935.

Her chamber music has received the most attention and one of her three string quartets, her Second String Quartet in G minor, Op.14 has entered the repertoire of many Scandinavian ensembles and was recorded on a Dacapo CD in 1999.
The parts and score to this work were  republished by Edition Silvertrust in June 2007.
W.W. Cobbett, Oxford University Press, London 1963
Notes to Dacapo Nancy Dalberg, CD 8.224138, Dacapo, Copenhagen, 1999
